'''Tranny chaser''' is an offensive phrase used to denote a person who loves or is attracted to [[transsexual]] or [[transgendered]] people.  It is usually applied to non-transgendered men who are attracted to pre- or non-operative [[transwomen]].  

See also [[Homosexuality and transgender]] for more information on the difficulty in defining relationships involving transgendered people as [[homosexuality|homosexual]] or [[heterosexuality|heterosexual]].

